OL,3,CLabour sets out plans to digitise
OL,4,Cchildren's healthcare records
OL,6,FLabour will digitise the NHS red book
OL,7,Fparents use for their children's
OL,8,Fmedical records as part of a series of
OL,9,Freforms to the NHS app.
OL,11,FParents and the NHS would be able to
OL,12,Fsee if children are behind on jabs or
OL,13,Fcheck-ups through a new digital
OL,14,Frecord, with automatic notifications
OL,15,Fto prompt them to book appointments
OL,16,Funder the party's plans.
OL,18,FThe red book has been handed out to
OL,19,Fnew parents for the past 30 years.
