OL,6,FPrevious health secretaries have hoped
OL,7,Fto digitise it during their tenure,
OL,8,Fincluding Jeremy Hunt and Matt
OL,9,FHancock, but so far the plans have not
OL,10,Fborne out.
OL,12,FLabour hopes its plans will help to
OL,13,Fboost MMR vaccination rates, which
OL,14,Fhave fallen in recent years.
OL,16,FMeasles outbreaks have at the same
OL,17,Ftime become more common.
