OL,3,CLabour sets out plans to digitise
OL,4,Cchildren's healthcare records
OL,6,FWes Streeting MP, Labour's shadow
OL,7,Fhealth secretary, said: "A child born
OL,8,Ftoday will live to see the 22nd
OL,9,Fcentury and things we can't begin to
OL,10,Fimagine. Labour wants them to be part
OL,11,Fof the healthiest generation that ever
OL,12,Flived. That's why we will digitise the
OL,13,Fred book, so children's health records
OL,14,Fare on the NHS App.
OL,16,F"This major step will transform
OL,17,Fchildren's healthcare and will mean
OL,18,Fmore children protected against
OL,19,Fmeasles. Now measles is back. It's
OL,20,Fhard to think of a clearer sign of
OL,21,FBritain's decline under the Tories.
