OL,6,F"With the red book on the app, the NHS
OL,7,Fwill be able to notify every parent of
OL,8,Fan unprotected child, give them
OL,9,Faccurate information about the MMR
OL,10,Fvaccine, and invite their child to get
OL,11,Fvaccinated. That's how a modern health
OL,12,Fservice would tackle this public
OL,13,Fhealth crisis."
OL,15,FWriting in the Sun newspaper, Mr
OL,16,FStreeting insisted the NHS was "a
OL,17,Fservice, not a shrine".
OL,19,FHe added: "It is judged by how well it
OL,20,Fserves the public, not how heavy a
OL,21,Fprice we're paying for failure.
