OL,6,F"The problems with the NHS are clear.
OL,7,FIt's a 20th century service that
OL,8,Fhasn't changed with the times and
OL,9,Fisn't fit for the modern era."
OL,11,FLabour will also commit to give
OL,12,Fpatients greater control over their
OL,13,Fown healthcare through the NHS app.
OL,15,FThis would include access to their
OL,16,Fmedical records on their phone,
OL,17,Fnotifications about screenings and
OL,18,Fvaccines they are eligible for, and
OL,19,Fbeing told what care they can expect
OL,20,Fwhen diagnosed with long-term
OL,21,Fconditions like asthma or diabetes.
