OL,6,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer claimed
OL,7,Fhis party would "give power to the
OL,8,Fpatient", and that GPs could ensure
OL,9,F"time isn't wasted on box-ticking".
OL,11,F"In 2024, patients still wait on the
OL,12,Fphone at 8am, or even queue up in
OL,13,Fperson, just to see a doctor. It's no
OL,14,Fwonder so many people don't bother or
OL,15,Fdon't have time, illness is caught too
OL,16,Flate, pressures on the NHS pile up,
OL,17,Fand lives are lost," he said.
